"dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.059424,0.096766,0.10924,0.11528,0.11113,0.10321,0.093452,0.079644,0.072504,0.066057,0.054692,0.038597],"unified_progress":[0.05981,0.091918,0.077217,0.10735,0.10948,0.10188,0.10274,0.087408,0.080189,0.072137,0.062288,0.047577]},{"section":7,"text":"This could mean bleeding somewhere in the upper part of the digestive system.","dimension":4,"group":6,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038711,0.070567,0.093383,0.11005,0.11392,0.11226,0.10607,0.094533,0.083963,0.076826,0.061886,0.037841],"unified_progress":[0.042621,0.074168,0.090899,0.10166,0.10268,0.10038,0.10105,0.095605,0.089557,0.081717,0.068168,0.051507]},{"section":8,"text":"His vitals are mostly stable, but his heart rate is up at 97 beats per minute.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.036692,0.072373,0.098647,0.12336,0.13129,0.12549,0.1107,0.089233,0.071405,0.061309,0.048044,0.031461],"unified_progress":[0.042206,0.078261,0.094312,0.1037,0.10868,0.10296,0.098165,0.09211,0.090349,0.073317,0.062645,0.053286]},{"section":9,"text":"That's a bit high, suggesting his body is under stress.","dimension":0,"group":7,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.038401,0.087651,0.1065,0.11988,0.12002,0.11541,0.10431,0.086814,0.075679,0.062362,0.050068,0.032912],"unified_progress":[0.043549,0.080129,0.096834,0.10405,0.10873,0.10042,0.10127,0.091173,0.086114,0.073603,0.063516,0.050617]},{"section":10,"text":"His blood pressure seems okay, though.","dimension":9,"group":1,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.032175,0.070731,0.098915,0.12493,0.13235,0.12569,0.11136,0.090613,0.073036,0.061961,0.047664,0.030578],"unified_progress":[0.040301,0.075323,0.092519,0.10422,0.10953,0.10333,0.10037,0.092212,0.093256,0.074053,0.062346,0.052537]},{"section":11,"text":"But wait, when I hear 'tense abdomen' and 'board-like rigidity,' my mind jumps to something really bad happening inside\u2014like maybe peritonitis, where the lining o